---
layout: default.njk
---

<div class="bg-[#111827]">
    {% include "header.html" %}
    <p class="font-fraunces text-white text-center text-5xl md:text-9xl pb-12 md:py-12 lg:py-24">Rooms & Suites</p>
</div>



<div class="mx-6 md:mx-[10%] lg:mx-[30%]">
    <div class="text-[#1A1A1A] text-sm md:text-xs text-center font-bold pt-24 md:pt-28 lg:pt-28 tracking-widest font-fraunces">WELCOME TO RAJ VILAS PALACE</div>
    <p class="primary-clr text-3xl md:text-4xl text-center  py-2 medium tracking-tight" style="line-height: 1.25;">Explore our refined accommodation options and find the perfect space for your stay.</p>
    <p class="text-sm md:text-base   text-center pb-8 md:pb-14">All rooms have a bathroom with bathtub and/or shower, cable television/radio, free WIFI and mini bar. In addition, all rooms are equipped with a Nespresso coffee machine. Most rooms are carpeted, some have parquet flooring.</p>
</div>

<div id="app" class="container mx-auto">
    <div class="options flex justify-center mb-4 gap-6 text-base md:text-base font-bold">
        <button class="option hover:primary-clr uppercase" @click="selectOption(0)" :class="{ 'yellow-underline': selectedOption === 0 }">Deluxe Suite</button>
        <button class="option hover:primary-clr uppercase" @click="selectOption(1)" :class="{ 'yellow-underline': selectedOption === 1 }">Royal Suite</button>
        <button class="option hover:primary-clr uppercase" @click="selectOption(2)" :class="{ 'yellow-underline': selectedOption === 2 }">Heritage Suite</button>
    </div>


    <div id="content">
    {% set i=0 %}
    {% for rm in page.roomssuites.room_type %}
        <div id="content-{{ i }}" class="content" v-show="selectedOption === {{ i }}">
            <div class="mx-[5%] md:mx-8 lg:mx-auto max-w-[400px] md:max-w-[900px] lg:max-w-[1300px]">
                <div class="flex-row md:inline-flex pt-10 md:pt-20 pb-8 md:pb-16 lg:pb-20 md:space-x-10">

                    <div class="flex-1 md:w-1/2">
                        <img src="{{rm.image}}" alt={{rm.title}} class="w-[650px] h-[467px]">
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex-1 md:mx-[1%] tracking-tight md:w-1/2">
                        <div class="md:pt-4 lg:pt-10">
                            <div class="mx-6 lg:py-8">
                                <p class="text-xs lg:pt-2 semibold whitespace-nowrap tracking-wider">WELCOME TO COZYSTAY APARTHOTEL</p>
                                <p class="primary-clr text-3xl md:text-5xl lg:pt-2 leading-snug medium whitespace-nowrap">{{rm.title}}</p>
                                <p class="text-gray-800 text-sm md:text-base  ">{{rm.desc}}</p>
                                <p class="primary-clr text-xs tracking-wider mt-6 md:mt-10">CALL US FOR MORE INFORMATION</p>
                                <button class="hover:primary-clr text-black text-2xl tracking-wider">+41 22 345 66 77</button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="flex justify-center">
                    <div class="min-w-screen-lg">
                        <div class="flex-row md:flex justify-between gap-11">
                            {% for t in page.roomssuites.rooms_list %}
                            {% if t.type == rm.title %}
                            <div class="">
                                <div style="overflow: hidden;">
                                    <img src="{{t.image}}" alt={{t.title}} class="w-[404px] h-[269px] transition-transform hover:scale-105">
                                </div>
                                <div class="mt-4 w-[404px] text-center">
                                    <h3 class="text-3xl font-fraunces">{{t.title}}</h3>
                                    <p class="primary-clr text-sm">{{t.spec}}</p>
                                    <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-gray-600 ">{{t.desc}}</p>
                                    <button class="primary-clr hover:text-black text-sm md:text-base mt-2 md:mt-4">
                                        <a href={{t.link}} class="hover:no-underline">Discover More â†’ </a>
                                    </button>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            {% endif %}
                            {% endfor %}
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
         {% set i = i + 1 %}
         {% endfor %}
    </div>
    
</div>

<div class="bg-[#EAE3DC]">
    <div class="justify-center max-w-[400px] md:max-w-[850px] lg:max-w-[1300px] mx-8 lg:mx-auto mt-20 md:mt-24 py-10">
        <div class="flex-row md:flex md:gap-20 lg:gap-40">
            <div class="md:w-1/2">
                <div class="text-xs">THE ESSENTIAL IN-ROOM AMENITIES</div>
                <div class="text-2xl md:text-4xl medium mt-4 md:mt-6">Our spaces have all the essentials you need for your stay.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-sm md:text-base text-gray-600 md:w-1/2 mt-8 md:mt-10">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetuer adipiscing elit. Aenean commodo ligula eget dolor. Aenean massa. Cum sociis natoque penatibus et magnis dis parturient montes, nascetur ridiculus mus. Donec quam felis, ultricies nec.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-left md:justify-center mt-8 md:mt-12 lg:mt-16">
